claim.claim-text:
The refrigerator of one of the claims 7 to 12, wherein the supporting member (150) comprises:
an elastic member fixing portion (151) formed on an upper surface of the supporting member (150) to fix the elastic member (130);
a plurality of air holes (153) formed through the supporting member (150) in a thickness direction of the supporting member (150);
a frame fixedly (151a) adhered onto a second contact portion (105b) of the casing; and
a plurality of supporting legs (151b) extending from the frame (151a) toward a central portion of the supporting member (150),
wherein the supporting member (150) fixedly supports the elastic member fixing portion (151) on an inner circumferential surface of the casing.
